Darkness Radio invites YouTubers Brennen Taylor & Jake Taylor to Share Ur Scare!

Paranormal explorers, brothers and popular YouTube stars join Dave & Tim to discuss their upcoming show, their scariest moments, locations and strange encounters.

Check out their site here: https://bit.ly/34i1fDn
